      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done at a great price? This vehicle is a solid, honest performer that has been well-loved and is ready for its next chapter. While it shows some expected signs of use and character on the interior and exterior, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking value and functionality. It\u2019s a fantastic opportunity to own a capable car without the premium price tag!",
